title: 007: Tales from the Gym
description: Sal, Adam and Justin have years of combined experience working in and managing gyms. Needless to say, they have witnessed some very strange (and sometimes downright disturbing) behavior over the years. In this episode they detail some of the weirdest things they have seen.
